data.title: In Memory Of
data.text:
This page was created to remember and honor faculty and alumni that are deceased. The list may be helpful to those that don't live in the Caro area anymore and to those that plan class reunions, etc. Your help is needed to make the list complete! If you know of someone that is not listed, please e-mail their name, their graduating class if you know it, and the year they passed away to sdwyer@carok12.org. The information on this page has been received from several different sources; I apologize if there are errors and ask that you email me with corrections.

Thank you, Scott Dwyer
